"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-09-More-exciting-events-to-follow-on-August-9-at-2024-Paris-Olympics-1vVm0xwhCW4-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  At the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics, Friday's late medal event schedule includes the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around final at 14:30 (GMT+2).  In table tennis, China will face Sweden in the men's team final at 15:00 (GMT+2).  In diving, China's Chen Yiwen and Chang Yani will battle for the individual gold medal in the women's 3m springboard at 15:00 (GMT+2).  And China's women's field hockey team has returned to the final after 16 years, and will meet the Netherlands in the gold medal contest at 20:00 (GMT+2).  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"